data.title: About: Ben Chapman (politician)
data.meta_description: James Keith Chapman (born 8 July 1940), known as Ben Chapman, is a British Labour Party politician and former civil servant who was the Member of Parliament (MP) for Wirral South from 1997 to 2010.
data.text:
dbo:abstract

بين شابمان (بالإنجليزية: Ben Chapman)‏ هو سياسي بريطاني، ولد في 8 يوليو 1940 في المملكة المتحدة. حزبياً، نشط في حزب العمال. (ar)

James Keith Chapman (born 8 July 1940), known as Ben Chapman, is a British Labour Party politician and former civil servant who was the Member of Parliament (MP) for Wirral South from 1997 to 2010. (en)

James Keith Chapman (känd som Ben Chapman), född 8 juli 1940, är en brittisk Labourpolitiker. Han var parlamentsledamot för valkretsen Wirral South från 1997 till 2010. Denna artikel om en brittisk politiker saknar väsentlig information. Du kan hjälpa till genom att lägga till den. (sv)
